text: Ronette Cort (born 24 May 1979) is a Guyanese former footballer who played as a goalkeeper. She has been a member of the Guyana women's national team. ==International career== Cort capped for Guyana at senior level during the 2010 CONCACAF Women's World Cup Qualifying qualification. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Guyanese women's footballers Category:Guyana women's international footballers
